description:
Panel discussion on the prevention of gun violence in Ohio.
Panelists include:
Erick Bellomy a Survivor Of Gun Violence; 
Tara Talgar from Moms Demand Actions;
Adrienne Hood, the mother of Henry Green; 
Yolanda Frierson a gun violence survivor from the Columbus CARE Coalition and Columbus Department Of Heath; and  
Crystal Turner, Motivational Speaker, Survivor, and The New Normal Documentary Producer.
